---
const stepsData = [
  {
    id: 1,
    title: "Instalar Windows Terminal y PowerShell",
    content: `
      <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm mb-1">¿Qué es Windows Terminal?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Windows Terminal es una aplicación moderna de terminal para Windows que permite usar PowerShell y otras terminales de forma más cómoda y visual.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-bold">1.1</span>
        Instalar desde Microsoft Store
      </h3>
      <ol class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">1</span>
          <span>Abre la <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Microsoft Store</strong> en tu computadora</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">2</span>
          <span>En el buscador, escribe: <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-mono text-xs">Windows Terminal</code></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">3</span>
          <span>Busca la app de <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Microsoft Corporation</strong></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">4</span>
          <span>Click en <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">"Instalar"</strong></span>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-bold">1.2</span>
        Instalar PowerShell
      </h3>
      <ol class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">1</span>
          <span>En Microsoft Store, busca: <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-mono text-xs">PowerShell</code></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">2</span>
          <span>Instala <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">"PowerShell"</strong> (la versión más reciente)</span>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-bold">1.3</span>
        Abrir Windows Terminal
      </h3>
      <ol class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">1</span>
          <span>Presiona la tecla <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Windows</strong> en tu teclado</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">2</span>
          <span>Escribe <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-mono text-xs">Terminal</code> o <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-mono text-xs">Windows Terminal</code></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">3</span>
          <span>Click en el icono para abrirlo</span>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-900 rounded-xl">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 mb-2">Verás algo como:</p>
        <code class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm">PS C:\\Users\\TU_USUARIO&gt;</code>
      </div>
    `
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    title: "Instalar Node.js",
    content: `
      <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm mb-1">¿Qué es Node.js?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Node.js es un programa necesario para ejecutar OpenCode y otras herramientas de desarrollo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3">Descargar Node.js</h3>
      <ol class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">1</span>
          <span>Abre tu navegador (Edge, Chrome, etc.)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">2</span>
          <span>Ve a: <a href="https://nodejs.org/" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:underline font-medium">nodejs.org</a></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">3</span>
          <span>Click en el botón <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">"LTS"</strong> (Recommended for most users)</span>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3">Verificar instalación</h3>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-900 rounded-lg">
          <code class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm">node --version</code>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Deberías ver algo como <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-mono text-xs">v20.18.0</code></p>
        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-900 rounded-lg">
          <code class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm">npm --version</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    `
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    title: "Instalar pnpm",
    content: `
      <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm mb-1">¿Qué es pnpm?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">pnpm es un administrador de paquetes más rápido y eficiente que npm.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-3 bg-slate-900 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <code class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm">npm install -g pnpm</code>
      </div>

      <div class="p-4 bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/30 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800 rounded-xl mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm mb-1">Solución de problemas</h4>
            <p class="text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm mb-2">Si aparece error de "permiso denegado", escribe primero:</p>
            <code class="text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-300 font-mono text-sm bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/50 px-2 py-1 rounded block">Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-3 bg-slate-900 rounded-lg">
        <code class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm">pnpm --version</code>
      </div>
    `
  },
  {
    id: 4,
    title: "Instalar OpenCode",
    content: `
      <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm mb-1">¿Qué es OpenCode?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">OpenCode es una aplicación de código abierto que permite chatear con IA mientras trabajas en proyectos de código.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3">Instalar OpenCode</h3>
      <div class="p-3 bg-slate-900 rounded-lg mb-4">
        <code class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm">pnpm install -g opencode-ai</code>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3">Verificar</h3>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-900 rounded-lg">
          <code class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm">opencode --version</code>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Si ves un número de versión, ¡la instalación fue exitosa!</p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3 mt-6">Abrir OpenCode</h3>
      <div class="p-3 bg-slate-900 rounded-lg">
        <code class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm">opencode</code>
      </div>
    `
  },
  {
    id: 5,
    title: "Conectar MiniMax.io como proveedor",
    content: `
      <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm mb-1">¿Qué es un proveedor?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Un proveedor es el servicio de IA que OpenCode usa para generar respuestas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
